{"_id":"GrS5T8tw0lDGQd01","name":"Shantak","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3},"type":"creature","data":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strengh","formula":"(4D6+20)*5"},"con":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":"(2D6+6)*5"},"siz":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":"(4D6+36)*5"},"dex":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":"(2D6+3)*5"},"app":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.APP","label":"CHARAC.Appearance","formula":""},"int":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.INT","label":"CHARAC.Intelligence","formula":"(1D6)*5"},"pow":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.POW","label":"CHARAC.Power","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"edu":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.EDU","label":"CHARAC.Education","formula":""}},"attribs":{"hp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Hit points","auto":true},"mp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Magic points","auto":true},"lck":{"value":null,"short":"LCK","label":"Luck","max":99},"san":{"value":null,"max":99,"short":"SAN","label":"Sanity","auto":true},"mov":{"value":"6 / 18 (volant)","short":"MOV","label":"Movement rate","auto":false},"db":{"value":null,"short":"DB","label":"Damage bonus","auto":true},"build":{"value":null,"short":"BLD","label":"Build","auto":true},"armor":{"value":9,"auto":false}},"status":{"criticalWounds":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"unconscious":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dying":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dead":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"prone":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"tempoInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"indefInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"personalDescription":{"type":"string","value":""},"special":{"attribs":{"move":{"primary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null},"secondary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null}}},"sanLoss":{"checkPassed":"0","checkFailled":"1D6"},"attacksPerRound":1},"infos":{"type":""},"flags":{"locked":true,"initialized":true,"displayFormula":false},"biography":{"personalDescription":{"value":"<p><em>Rien &agrave; voir avec les oiseaux ou les chauvessouris que l&rsquo;on trouve sur terre&hellip; ils &eacute;taient plus gros que des &eacute;l&eacute;phants, avec une t&ecirc;te digne d&rsquo;un cheval&hellip; L&rsquo;oiseau-shantak &eacute;tait couvert d&rsquo;&eacute;cailles plut&ocirc;t que de plumes, et des &eacute;cailles tr&egrave;s glissantes. </em></p>\n<p>&mdash; H. P. Lovecraft, La Qu&ecirc;te onirique de Kadath l&rsquo;inconnue&nbsp;</p>\n<p>D&eacute;crits comme bruyants et hideux, les shantaks occupent de vastes cavernes, o&ugrave; leurs ailes poisseuses sont macul&eacute;es de moisissure et de salp&ecirc;tre. Les serviteurs des Dieux Ext&eacute;rieurs les dressent en tant que montures. Toutefois, ils craignent les maigres b&ecirc;tes de la nuit, qu&rsquo;ils fuient &agrave; vue. On a d&eacute;j&agrave; vu un shantak, capable de voler dans l&rsquo;espace, emporter un cavalier imprudent jusqu&rsquo;au tr&ocirc;ne d&rsquo;Azathoth.</p>\n<p><strong>Perte de Sant&eacute; Mentale : </strong>0/1D6</p>\n<h3>Pouvoirs distinctifs</h3>\n<p><strong>Sortil&egrave;ges : </strong>aucun</p>\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p><strong>Attaques par round :</strong> 1</p>\n<p><strong>Options de Combat rapproch&eacute; :</strong> Ces grands monstres peuvent donner des coups ou mordre leurs adversaires.</p>\n<p><strong>Mordre et tenir (man&oelig;uvre) : </strong>Ils peuvent maintenir un adversaire mordu dans leur gueule.</p>\n<p><strong>Protection : </strong>9 points (peau)</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Shantak.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Shantak","displayName":0,"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Shantak.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"GrS5T8tw0lDGQd01","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"8BxcZb4nO7pzTCUf","name":"Combat rapproché","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"45","attributes":{},"properties":{"combat":true,"fighting":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":100000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"p8WLiRSmm1d5Ehah","name":"Queue","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"Creature's natural attack","chat":"Creature's natural attack","special":""},"wpnType":"innate","skill":{"main":{"name":"Fighting","id":"8BxcZb4nO7pzTCUf"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""}},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":"1D6"},"long":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"extreme":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""}},"usesPerRound":{"normal":1,"max":null,"burst":null},"bullets":null,"ammo":0,"malfunction":null,"blastRadius":null,"properties":{"addb":true,"slnt":false,"melee":true,"rngd":false},"eras":{},"price":{}},"sort":200000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"g5aN7C5MrXs0t7yY","name":"Esquive","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"<p>Comp&eacute;tence primordiale, elle permet d&rsquo;&eacute;viter les coups, les armes de jet et d&rsquo;autres attaques dangereuses. Un investigateur peut esquiver autant de fois que n&eacute;cessaire dans le m&ecirc;me round de combat, mais une seule fois par attaque (cf. Chapitre 6 : Combat). Toutefois, il ne peut esquiver que les attaques qu&rsquo;il voit venir. Ainsi, il est impossible d&rsquo;esquiver les balles, puisqu&rsquo;on ne les voit plus bouger une fois en mouvement. Le mieux que l&rsquo;on peut faire est de prendre des mesures d&eacute;fensives, pour se rendre plus difficile &agrave; toucher (cf. Se mettre &agrave; couvert, page 100).</p>\n<p>L&rsquo;Esquive progresse avec l&rsquo;exp&eacute;rience, comme n&rsquo;importe quelle comp&eacute;tence.</p>\n<h2>Comp&eacute;tence oppos&eacute;e / Niveau de difficult&eacute; :</h2>\n<p>Servant essentiellement lors de tests oppos&eacute;s en combat, l&rsquo;esquive n&rsquo;a pas de difficult&eacute; fixe.</p>\n<p><strong> Note :</strong> En tant que comp&eacute;tence de combat, le redoublement est impossible.</p>","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":"@DEX/2","adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"25","attributes":{},"properties":{"fighting":false,"firearm":false,"combat":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":300000,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]},{"_id":"u6h0QzZJ1Wt02QEM","name":"Morsure","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"","chat":"","special":""},"wpnType":"","skill":{"main":{"name":"","id":"8BxcZb4nO7pzTCUf"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""}},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":"2D6+2"},"long":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"extreme":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""}},"usesPerRound":{"normal":"1","max":"","burst":null},"bullets":"","ammo":0,"malfunction":"","blastRadius":null,"properties":{"melee":true,"rngd":false,"thrown":false,"shotgun":false,"dbrl":false,"impl":false,"brst":false,"auto":false,"ahdb":false,"addb":false,"slnt":false,"spcl":true,"mont":false,"blst":false,"stun":false,"rare":false,"burn":false},"eras":{"1920":false,"nvct":false,"drka":false,"ddts":false,"glit":false,"pulp":false,"mdrn":false},"price":{}},"sort":400000,"flags":{},"effects":[]}],"effects":[]}
{"_id":"Gs8PTThxfaHWUK0M","name":"Maigre bête de la nuit","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3},"type":"creature","data":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":25,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strengh","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"con":{"value":50,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"siz":{"value":60,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":"(4D6)*5"},"dex":{"value":60,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":"(2D6+6)*5"},"app":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.APP","label":"CHARAC.Appearance","formula":""},"int":{"value":30,"short":"CHARAC.INT","label":"CHARAC.Intelligence","formula":"1D6*5"},"pow":{"value":60,"short":"CHARAC.POW","label":"CHARAC.Power","formula":"3d6*5"},"edu":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.EDU","label":"CHARAC.Education","formula":""}},"attribs":{"hp":{"value":11,"max":11,"short":"HP","label":"Hit points","auto":true},"mp":{"value":12,"max":12,"short":"HP","label":"Magic points","auto":true},"lck":{"value":null,"short":"LCK","label":"Luck","max":99},"san":{"value":60,"max":99,"short":"SAN","label":"Sanity","auto":true},"mov":{"value":"6 / 12 (volant)","short":"MOV","label":"Movement rate","auto":false},"db":{"value":null,"short":"DB","label":"Damage bonus","auto":true},"build":{"value":null,"short":"BLD","label":"Build","auto":true},"armor":{"value":2,"auto":false}},"status":{"criticalWounds":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"unconscious":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dying":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dead":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"prone":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"tempoInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"indefInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"personalDescription":{"type":"string","value":""},"special":{"attribs":{"move":{"primary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null},"secondary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null}}},"sanLoss":{"checkPassed":"0","checkFailled":"1D6"},"attacksPerRound":1},"infos":{"type":""},"flags":{"locked":true,"initialized":true,"displayFormula":false},"biography":{"personalDescription":{"value":"<p><em>Noires choses repoussantes et grotesques ayant un &eacute;piderme doux et huileux comme en ont les baleines, d&rsquo;affreuses cornes courb&eacute;es l&rsquo;une vers l&rsquo;autre, des ailes de chauve-souris dont le battement ne faisait pas de bruit, d&rsquo;ignobles pattes pr&eacute;hensiles et des queues poilues qu&rsquo;elles balan&ccedil;aient continuellement. Le pire de tout &eacute;tait qu&rsquo;elles ne parlaient jamais et ne riaient jamais, car elles n&rsquo;avaient pas de visage qui leur e&ucirc;t permis de sourire, mais seulement un vide suggestif qui devait leur en tenir lieu. Elles n&rsquo;&eacute;taient capables que de saisir, de voler et de pincer, car tel est le destin des maigres b&ecirc;tes de la nuit. </em></p>\n<p>&mdash; H. P. Lovecraft, La Qu&ecirc;te onirique de Kadath l&rsquo;inconnue&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Les maigres b&ecirc;tes de la nuit sont des cr&eacute;atures des Contr&eacute;es du R&ecirc;ve au service de Nodens, pour le compte duquel, entre autres choses, elles se saisissent des importuns et les emm&egrave;nent dans les lieux les plus lugubres et r&eacute;pugnants que l&rsquo;on puisse imaginer, afin qu&rsquo;ils y meurent. Elles vivent en divers endroits parmi les plus recul&eacute;s des Contr&eacute;es du R&ecirc;ve, d&rsquo;o&ugrave; elles ne sortent que la nuit. En des temps primitifs, elles vivaient aussi dans le Monde de l&rsquo;&Eacute;veil, et peut-&ecirc;tre est-ce encore le cas. Bien qu&rsquo;elles ne soient pas tr&egrave;s intelligentes, elles semblent n&eacute;anmoins comprendre certaines langues (comme le couinement des goules) et entretiennent de bonnes relations avec certaines races occultes.</p>\n<p><strong>Perte de Sant&eacute; Mentale :</strong> 0/1D6</p>\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p><strong>Attaques par round : </strong>1</p>\n<p><strong>Options de Combat rapproch&eacute; : </strong>Elles attaquent avec leurs pattes, leurs queues, leurs cornes ou leurs membres.</p>\n<p><strong>Saisir (man&oelig;uvre) : </strong>Une tactique fr&eacute;quente des maigres b&ecirc;tes de la nuit consiste &agrave; saisir leur adversaire, afin de pouvoir le &laquo; titiller &raquo; avec leur queue poilue. Elles attaquent par surprise et en masse, puis d&eacute;robent les armes de leurs ennemis avant de les submerger. Deux b&ecirc;tes ou plus peuvent combiner leurs attaques pour maintenir une victime trop costaude et profiter d&rsquo;un d&eacute; bonus de surnombre.</p>\n<p><strong>Titiller : </strong>Une sombre b&ecirc;te ne peut titiller qu&rsquo;un ennemi qu&rsquo;elle vient de saisir. Ce mode d&rsquo;attaque est particuli&egrave;rement &eacute;nervant, car les poils de leur queue sont aussi tranchants que des rasoirs et repr&eacute;sentent un r&eacute;el danger, m&ecirc;me s&rsquo;ils n&rsquo;infligent pas de dommages. La victime, d&eacute;sorient&eacute;e et humili&eacute;e, ne peut alors plus penser &agrave; autre chose qu&rsquo;&agrave; la menace qui p&egrave;se sur elle, ce qui impose un d&eacute; malus &agrave; toutes ses actions pendant 1D4 rounds ou jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; ce que les chatouilles cessent. Les b&ecirc;tes de la nuit savent parfaitement tirer parti des trous dans les v&ecirc;tements. Des habits &eacute;pais ou une armure ne sont d&rsquo;aucune utilit&eacute; face &agrave; ce type d&rsquo;attaque.</p>\n<p><strong>Protection : </strong>2 points (peau)</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Nightgaunt.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Maigre bête de la nuit","displayName":0,"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Nightgaunt.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"Gs8PTThxfaHWUK0M","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"13JzC1eVfTeBbJx3","name":"Combat rapproché","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"45","attributes":{},"properties":{"combat":true,"fighting":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":100000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"UxLBgXzwAmA9c5dY","name":"Pattes","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"Creature's natural attack","chat":"Creature's natural attack","special":""},"wpnType":"innate","skill":{"main":{"name":"Fighting","id":"13JzC1eVfTeBbJx3"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""}},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":"1D4"},"long":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"extreme":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""}},"usesPerRound":{"normal":1,"max":null,"burst":null},"bullets":null,"ammo":0,"malfunction":null,"blastRadius":null,"properties":{"addb":true,"slnt":false,"melee":true,"rngd":false},"eras":{},"price":{}},"sort":200000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"q9XqzdPtSOQwuSeq","name":"Combat spécial","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"35","attributes":{},"properties":{"special":true,"rarity":false,"push":true,"combat":true,"fighting":true,"firearm":false},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":300000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"Wg72dznlUEPwLTCG","name":"Discrétion","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"","description":{"value":"<p>L’art de se déplacer sans faire de bruit ni se faire voir. Lorsqu’un investigateur souhaite éviter d’être repéré, le joueur doit faire un test de Discrétion. Un niveau de compétence élevé signifie que le personnage est doué pour marcher en silence et se camoufler, ou qu’il a suffisamment de nerfs et de patience pour rester immobile pendant de longues périodes.</p>\n<h2>Compétence opposée / Niveau de difficulté :</h2>\n<p>Lorsqu’un investigateur se cache, la difficulté de son test de Discrétion est déterminée sur la base de la compétence écouter ou Trouver Objet Caché de ses adversaires. Elle peut être modifiée selon la situation (ténèbres, bruits).</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Difficulté ordinaire : se déplacer silencieusement dans une maison sans se faire entendre par des personnes moyennes (dont les compétences écouter et Trouver Objet Caché sont inférieures à 50 %).</li>\n<li>Difficulté majeure : ne pas se faire repérer par un chien de garde attentif ; se cacher en n’ayant que quelques secondes devant soi.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Comment redoubler ?</h2>\n<p>Prendre le temps d’étudier les lieux ; retirer ses chaussures ; faire diversion ; ne plus bouger le temps que les choses se calment.</p>\n<h2>Conséquences d’un redoublement raté ?</h2>\n<p>Sans le savoir, l’investigateur a été repéré par les adorateurs, mais plutôt que de s’en prendre à lui directement, ils ont décidé d’invoquer une créature qui va s’occuper de lui ; quelqu’un ferme à clef la porte du placard où l’investigateur vient de se réfugier, puis la cloue au chambranle.</p>\n<p>Si un investigateur dément rate un redoublement, il peut se croire invisible, alors que tout le monde peut le voir.</p>","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":"20","adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"90","attributes":{},"properties":{"push":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":400000,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]},{"_id":"zl4uK2tvd2oq5ABI","name":"Saisie","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"","chat":"","special":""},"wpnType":"","skill":{"main":{"name":"","id":"13JzC1eVfTeBbJx3"},"alternat