{"_id":"KnKxU7DNW0NJvmeT","name":"Byakhee","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3},"type":"creature","data":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":75,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strengh","formula":"5d6*5"},"con":{"value":35,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":"3d6*5"},"siz":{"value":70,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":"5d6*5"},"dex":{"value":45,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":"(3d6+3)*5"},"app":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.APP","label":"CHARAC.Appearance","formula":""},"int":{"value":60,"short":"CHARAC.INT","label":"CHARAC.Intelligence","formula":"3d6*5"},"pow":{"value":55,"short":"CHARAC.POW","label":"CHARAC.Power","formula":"3d6*5"},"edu":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.EDU","label":"CHARAC.Education","formula":""}},"attribs":{"hp":{"value":10,"max":10,"short":"HP","label":"Hit points","auto":true},"mp":{"value":10,"max":11,"short":"HP","label":"Magic points","auto":true},"lck":{"value":null,"short":"LCK","label":"Luck","max":99},"san":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"SAN","label":"Sanity","auto":true,"dailyLoss":49},"mov":{"value":"5 / 16 (vol)","short":"MOV","label":"Movement rate","auto":false},"db":{"value":"","short":"DB","label":"Damage bonus","auto":true},"build":{"value":2,"short":"BLD","label":"Build","auto":false},"armor":{"value":2,"auto":false}},"status":{"criticalWounds":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"unconscious":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dying":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dead":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"prone":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"tempoInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"indefInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"personalDescription":{"type":"string","value":""},"special":{"attribs":{"move":{"primary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null},"secondary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null}}},"sanLoss":{"checkPassed":"1","checkFailled":"1D6"},"attacksPerRound":1},"infos":{"type":""},"flags":{"locked":true,"initialized":true,"displayFormula":false},"biography":{"personalDescription":{"value":"<p><em>Arriva une horde de choses ail&eacute;es, apprivois&eacute;es et hybrides&hellip; Ce n&rsquo;&eacute;tait ni compl&egrave;tement des corneilles, ni des taupes, ni des fourmis, ni des vampires, ni des &ecirc;tres humains en d&eacute;composition, mais quelque chose dont je ne peux, ni ne dois, me souvenir.&nbsp;</em></p>\n<p>H. P. Lovecraft, Le Festival</p>\n<p>Essentiellement d&eacute;vou&eacute;e &agrave; Hastur l&rsquo;Indicible, cette race interstellaire peut &ecirc;tre invoqu&eacute;e pour contribuer &agrave; des rituels. Compos&eacute;s de mati&egrave;re conventionnelle, bien qu&rsquo;&eacute;trangement organis&eacute;s, ces &ecirc;tres sont vuln&eacute;rables aux armes ordinaires, telles que les pistolets. Habitants du vide interstellaire, les byakhees ne poss&egrave;dent pas de base permanente sur notre Terre, mais sont fr&eacute;quemment invoqu&eacute;s pour accomplir certaines missions ou pour servir de montures stellaires.</p>\n<p><strong>Perte de Sant&eacute; Mentale :&nbsp;</strong>1/1D6</p>\n<h3>Pouvoirs distinctifs</h3>\n<p><strong>Vol : </strong>Un byakhee peut voler au travers de l&rsquo;espace interstellaire en transportant un passager, pourvu que ce dernier soit prot&eacute;g&eacute; du vide et du froid par un sort ou une potion appropri&eacute; (comme le Breuvage de l&rsquo;Espace).</p>\n<p><strong>Sortil&egrave;ges : </strong>Les byakhees ont 40 % de chances de conna&icirc;tre 1D4 sortil&egrave;ges. En principe, il s&rsquo;agit d&rsquo;enchantements relatifs &agrave; Hastur et aux cr&eacute;atures qui lui sont associ&eacute;es.</p>\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p><strong>Attaques par round :</strong> 2</p>\n<p><strong>Options de Combat rapproch&eacute; : </strong>Un byakhee frappe avec ses deux serres simultan&eacute;ment ou se pr&eacute;cipite sur sa victime pour lui infliger de terribles blessures.</p>\n<p><strong>Mordre et serrer (man&oelig;uvre) : </strong>Si la morsure atteint son but, le byakhee reste accroch&eacute; &agrave; sa proie et commence &agrave; lui sucer le sang. Cette succion absorbe alors 3D10 points de FOR par round, jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; ce que mort s&rsquo;ensuive (quand la FOR tombe &agrave; 0). La victime du byakhee a droit &agrave; un test oppos&eacute; de FOR pour &eacute;chapper &agrave; ce sort funeste. Habituellement, la chose ne l&acirc;che pas sa proie d&rsquo;elle-m&ecirc;me. Un byakhee ne peut immobiliser qu&rsquo;une victime &agrave; la fois. Les survivants r&eacute;cup&egrave;rent leur sang (et les points de FOR aff&eacute;rents) en se reposant ou par transfusion sanguine, dans la limite de 1D10+5 points par jour.</p>\n<p><strong>Protection :</strong> 2 points (fourrure et cuir &eacute;pais)</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"cthulhu","system":"CoC7","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.2.4"}},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Byakhee.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Byakhee","displayName":0,"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Byakhee-2.png","tint":"","width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"mirrorX":false,"mirrorY":false,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightColor":"","lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"KnKxU7DNW0NJvmeT","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":""},"bar2":{"attribute":""},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"RU1pwcNorBHg8hNf","name":"Combat rapproché","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"55","attributes":{},"properties":{"combat":true,"fighting":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"so