{"_id":"O8lzGcVzCNSWVUel","name":"Profond","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3},"type":"creature","data":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strengh","formula":"(4D6)*5"},"con":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"siz":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":"(3D6+6)*5"},"dex":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"app":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.APP","label":"CHARAC.Appearance","formula":""},"int":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.INT","label":"CHARAC.Intelligence","formula":"(2D6+6)*5"},"pow":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.POW","label":"CHARAC.Power","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"edu":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.EDU","label":"CHARAC.Education","formula":""}},"attribs":{"hp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Hit points","auto":true},"mp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Magic points","auto":true},"lck":{"value":null,"short":"LCK","label":"Luck","max":99},"san":{"value":null,"max":99,"short":"SAN","label":"Sanity","auto":true},"mov":{"value":"8 / 10 (nageant)","short":"MOV","label":"Movement rate","auto":false},"db":{"value":null,"short":"DB","label":"Damage bonus","auto":true},"build":{"value":null,"short":"BLD","label":"Build","auto":true},"armor":{"value":1,"auto":false}},"status":{"criticalWounds":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"unconscious":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dying":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dead":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"prone":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"tempoInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"indefInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"personalDescription":{"type":"string","value":""},"special":{"attribs":{"move":{"primary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null},"secondary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null}}},"sanLoss":{"checkPassed":"0","checkFailled":"1D6"},"attacksPerRound":1},"infos":{"type":""},"flags":{"locked":true,"initialized":true,"displayFormula":false},"biography":{"personalDescription":{"value":"<p><em>Ils &eacute;taient de couleur verd&acirc;tre et avaient le ventre blanc. Leur peau semblait luisante et lisse, mais leur &eacute;chine se h&eacute;rissait d&rsquo;&eacute;cailles. Leur corps vaguement anthropo&iuml;de se terminait par une t&ecirc;te de poisson aux yeux saillants toujours ouverts. Sur le c&ocirc;t&eacute; de leur cou s&rsquo;ouvraient des ou&iuml;es palpitantes et leurs longues pattes &eacute;taient palm&eacute;es. Ils avan&ccedil;aient par bonds irr&eacute;guliers, tant&ocirc;t sur deux pattes, tant&ocirc;t sur quatre&hellip; Leur voix coassante&hellip; avait toutes les nuances d&rsquo;expression dont leur visage &eacute;tait d&eacute;pourvu. </em></p>\n<p>&mdash; H. P. Lovecraft, Le Cauchemar d&rsquo;Innsmouth</p>\n<p>Les Profonds forment une race amphibie dont la principale fonction consiste &agrave; servir Cthulhu et deux &ecirc;tres connus sous les noms de P&egrave;re Dagon et M&egrave;re Hydra. Confin&eacute;s dans les abysses intemporelles, ils m&egrave;nent une existence arrogante et quasi illimit&eacute;e, o&ugrave; se m&ecirc;lent froide beaut&eacute; et cruaut&eacute; inimaginable. Ils se r&eacute;unissent pour procr&eacute;er ou adorer le Grand Cthulhu, mais ne cherchent pas le contact physique comme les humains. Ce sont des cr&eacute;atures exclusivement marines, on ne les rencontre jamais en eau douce. Ils poss&egrave;dent de nombreuses cit&eacute;s immerg&eacute;es, dont une se trouve au large du Massachusetts, pr&egrave;s d&rsquo;Innsmouth et d&rsquo;autres seraient non loin de l&rsquo;Angleterre.</p>\n<p>Ils sont parfois v&eacute;n&eacute;r&eacute;s par des humains d&eacute;sireux de s&rsquo;accoupler avec eux, car ils sont virtuellement immortels, ne connaissant que rarement une mort naturelle, et les hybrides n&eacute;s de leurs unions contre-nature conf&egrave;rent &agrave; leurs adeptes une sorte de p&eacute;rennit&eacute; &eacute;ternelle.</p>\n<p><strong>Perte de Sant&eacute; Mentale : </strong>0/1D6</p>\n<h3>Pouvoirs distinctifs</h3>\n<p><strong>Respiration aquatique : </strong>Habitants des oc&eacute;ans, les Profonds n&rsquo;ont besoin d&rsquo;aucune aide ext&eacute;rieure pour respirer sous l&rsquo;eau. Amphibies, ils sont &eacute;galement &agrave; l&rsquo;aise &agrave; la surface.</p>\n<p><strong>Sortil&egrave;ges :</strong> Un Profond a 40 % de chances de conna&icirc;tre 1D4 sorts.</p>\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p><strong>Attaques par round : </strong>1</p>\n<p><strong>Options de Combat rapproch&eacute; : </strong>Les Profonds manient des armes, comme les humains. Ils affichent une certaine pr&eacute;f&eacute;rence pour les harpons et les tridents.</p>\n<p><strong>Protection :</strong> 1 point (peau et &eacute;cailles)</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Deep%20One.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Profond","displayName":0,"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Deep%20One.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"O8lzGcVzCNSWVUel","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"XxeklFZ549iH3vP3","name":"Combat rapproché","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"45","attributes":{},"properties":{"combat":true,"fighting":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":100000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"tuRAh2etS3BhD7rA","name":"Trident","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"Creature's natural attack","chat":"Creature's natural attack","special":""},"wpnType":"innate","skill":{"main":{"name":"Fighting","id":"XxeklFZ549iH3vP3"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""}},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":"1D8"},"long":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"extreme":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""}},"usesPerRound":{"normal":1,"max":null,"burst":null},"bullets":null,"ammo":0,"malfunction":null,"blastRadius":null,"properties":{"addb":true,"slnt":false,"melee":true,"rngd":false},"eras":{},"price":{}},"sort":200000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"Puf0M8DI1tiD5b7D","name":"Esquive","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"<p>Comp&eacute;tence primordiale, elle permet d&rsquo;&eacute;viter les coups, les armes de jet et d&rsquo;autres attaques dangereuses. Un investigateur peut esquiver autant de fois que n&eacute;cessaire dans le m&ecirc;me round de combat, mais une seule fois par attaque (cf. Chapitre 6 : Combat). Toutefois, il ne peut esquiver que les attaques qu&rsquo;il voit venir. Ainsi, il est impossible d&rsquo;esquiver les balles, puisqu&rsquo;on ne les voit plus bouger une fois en mouvement. Le mieux que l&rsquo;on peut faire est de prendre des mesures d&eacute;fensives, pour se rendre plus difficile &agrave; toucher (cf. Se mettre &agrave; couvert, page 100).</p>\n<p>L&rsquo;Esquive progresse avec l&rsquo;exp&eacute;rience, comme n&rsquo;importe quelle comp&eacute;tence.</p>\n<h2>Comp&eacute;tence oppos&eacute;e / Niveau de difficult&eacute; :</h2>\n<p>Servant essentiellement lors de tests oppos&eacute;s en combat, l&rsquo;esquive n&rsquo;a pas de difficult&eacute; fixe.</p>\n<p><strong> Note :</strong> En tant que comp&eacute;tence de combat, le redoublement est impossible.</p>","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":"@DEX/2","adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"25","attributes":{},"proper