{"_id":"UUeidNGbaLZVvZr9","name":"Vampire de feu","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3},"type":"creature","data":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strengh","formula":""},"con":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":"(2D6)*5"},"siz":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":"1"},"dex":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":"(3D6+6)*5"},"app":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.APP","label":"CHARAC.Appearance","formula":""},"int":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.INT","label":"CHARAC.Intelligence","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"pow":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.POW","label":"CHARAC.Power","formula":"(2D6+6)*5"},"edu":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.EDU","label":"CHARAC.Education","formula":""}},"attribs":{"hp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Hit points","auto":true},"mp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Magic points","auto":true},"lck":{"value":null,"short":"LCK","label":"Luck","max":99},"san":{"value":null,"max":99,"short":"SAN","label":"Sanity","auto":true},"mov":{"value":"11","short":"MOV","label":"Movement rate","auto":false},"db":{"value":null,"short":"DB","label":"Damage bonus","auto":true},"build":{"value":null,"short":"BLD","label":"Build","auto":true},"armor":{"value":null,"auto":false}},"status":{"criticalWounds":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"unconscious":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dying":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dead":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"prone":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"tempoInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"indefInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"personalDescription":{"type":"string","value":""},"special":{"attribs":{"move":{"primary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null},"secondary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null}}},"sanLoss":{"checkPassed":"0","checkFailled":"1D6"},"attacksPerRound":1},"infos":{"type":""},"flags":{"locked":true,"initialized":true,"displayFormula":true},"biography":{"personalDescription":{"value":"<p><em>Alors apparurent des milliers de minuscules points lumineux&hellip; Ces myriades de points &eacute;taient des entit&eacute;s vivantes faites de flammes ! En effet, d&egrave;s qu&rsquo;elles touchaient quelque chose, cela prenait feu. </em></p>\n<p>&mdash; August Derleth, L&rsquo;Habitant de l&rsquo;ombre</p>\n<p>Serviteurs du Grand Ancien nomm&eacute; Cthugha, ces &ecirc;tres r&eacute;sident, comme lui, dans les parages de l&rsquo;&eacute;toile Fomalhaut. Ils ne viennent sur Terre que s&rsquo;ils sont invoqu&eacute;s ou lorsqu&rsquo;ils accompagnent leur ma&icirc;tre. Ils semblent &ecirc;tre une forme de gaz ou de plasma dou&eacute; d&rsquo;intelligence.</p>\n<p><strong>Perte de Sant&eacute; Mentale :</strong> 0/1D6</p>\n<h3>Pouvoirs distinctifs</h3>\n<p><strong>Sortil&egrave;ges : </strong>Un vampire de feu a 20 % de chances de conna&icirc;tre 1D3 sorts.</p>\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p><strong>Attaques par round :</strong> 1</p>\n<p><strong>Options de Combat rapproch&eacute; :</strong> Les vampires de feu combattent en touchant leurs adversaires et enflammant les objets inflammables. Ils infligent des br&ucirc;lures aux hommes qu&rsquo;ils touchent. Pour d&eacute;terminer l&rsquo;&eacute;tendue des dommages, lancez 2D6. Si la victime r&eacute;ussit un test de CON, elle n&rsquo;encaisse que la moiti&eacute; des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts normalement inflig&eacute;s par la br&ucirc;lure. Sinon, elle subit l&rsquo;int&eacute;gralit&eacute; des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts normaux. Au cours de la m&ecirc;me attaque, un vampire de feu tentera &eacute;galement de subtiliser des points de magie &agrave; sa victime. Pour cela, il effectue un test oppos&eacute; de POU. S&rsquo;il perd cette confrontation, il perd 1 point de magie. En revanche, s&rsquo;il l&rsquo;emporte, il vole 1D10 points de magie &agrave; sa victime. Par cons&eacute;quent, chaque fois qu&rsquo;un vampire de feu attaque, il faut effectuer deux tests : un pour d&eacute;terminer les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts dus &agrave; la chaleur et un autre pour savoir s&rsquo;il absorbe ou non des points de magie.</p>\n<p><strong>Protection : </strong>La plupart des armes mat&eacute;rielles (balles, lames, etc.) ne leur font pas de mal. L&rsquo;eau, par contre, leur inflige 1 point de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts par 2 litres de liquide d&eacute;vers&eacute; sur eux. Ainsi, un extincteur manuel standard leur d&eacute;livre 1D6 points de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts chaque fois qu&rsquo;il touche, et un seau d&rsquo;eau 1D3.</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Fire%20Vampire.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Vampire de feu","displayName":0,"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Fire%20Vampire.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"UUeidNGbaLZVvZr9","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"Zmo3PUcu62qq04EL","name":"Combat rapproché","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"85","attributes":{},"properties":{"combat":true,"fighting":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":100000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"NtMosZ7E1tWuNQHq","name":"Flammes","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"Creature's natural attack","chat":"Creature's natural attack","special":""},"wpnType":"innate","skill":{"main":{"name":"Fighting","id":"Zmo3PUcu62qq04EL"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""}},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","da