{"_id":"oGUilfb1xc3NJzK3","name":"Chose-rat","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3},"type":"creature","data":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":10,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strengh","formula":"1D3*5"},"con":{"value":60,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":"2D6*5"},"siz":{"value":5,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":"5"},"dex":{"value":90,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":"(4D6+4)*5"},"app":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.APP","label":"CHARAC.Appearance","formula":""},"int":{"value":35,"short":"CHARAC.INT","label":"CHARAC.Intelligence","formula":"3d6*5"},"pow":{"value":15,"short":"CHARAC.POW","label":"CHARAC.Power","formula":"2d6*5"},"edu":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.EDU","label":"CHARAC.Education","formula":""}},"attribs":{"hp":{"value":2,"max":6,"short":"HP","label":"Hit points","auto":true},"mp":{"value":3,"max":3,"short":"HP","label":"Magic points","auto":true},"lck":{"value":null,"short":"LCK","label":"Luck","max":99},"san":{"value":20,"max":99,"short":"SAN","label":"Sanity","auto":true},"mov":{"value":null,"short":"MOV","label":"Movement rate","auto":true},"db":{"value":"-2","short":"DB","label":"Damage bonus","auto":true},"build":{"value":-2,"short":"BLD","label":"Build","auto":false},"armor":{"value":null,"auto":false}},"status":{"criticalWounds":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"unconscious":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dying":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dead":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"prone":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"tempoInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"indefInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"personalDescription":{"type":"string","value":""},"special":{"attribs":{"move":{"primary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null},"secondary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null}}},"sanLoss":{"checkPassed":"0","checkFailled":"1D6"},"attacksPerRound":1},"infos":{"type":""},"flags":{"locked":true,"initialized":true,"displayFormula":false},"biography":{"personalDescription":{"value":"<p><em>Les os des pattes minuscules, dit-on, d&eacute;notent des facult&eacute;s de pr&eacute;hension plus caract&eacute;ristiques d&rsquo;un petit singe que d&rsquo;un rat ; tandis que le cr&acirc;ne aux f&eacute;roces crocs jaunes est absolument anormal, car vu sous certains angles, il para&icirc;t la caricature monstrueuse d&rsquo;un cr&acirc;ne humain en miniature. </em></p>\n<p>&mdash; H. P. Lovecraft, La Maison de la sorci&egrave;re</p>\n<p>Ces cr&eacute;atures aux longs crocs effil&eacute;s peuvent &ecirc;tre confondues avec des rats ordinaires lorsqu&rsquo;on les voit de loin. De plus pr&egrave;s, on remarque qu&rsquo;elles sont dot&eacute;es de t&ecirc;tes et de mains caricaturant celles des hommes.</p>\n<p>Il est possible qu&rsquo;elles soient cr&eacute;&eacute;es par des rituels de magie mal&eacute;fique, afin que des serviteurs d&eacute;funts rev&ecirc;tent cette forme et continuent ainsi &agrave; servir leurs ma&icirc;tres. On dit aussi de ces abominations qu&rsquo;elles sont vers&eacute;es dans les myst&egrave;res du Mythe de Cthulhu, et que les dieux noirs les mettent parfois au service de sorci&egrave;res ou de magiciens humains. Brown Jenkin, le familier de la sorci&egrave;re Keziah Mason, &eacute;tait l&rsquo;une de ces choses.</p>\n<p><strong>Perte de Sant&eacute; Mentale :</strong> 0/1D6 en g&eacute;n&eacute;ral ; 1/1D8 si l&rsquo;observateur connaissait la chose-rat avant sa transformation.</p>\n<h3>Pouvoirs distinctifs</h3>\n<p><strong>Sortil&egrave;ges :</strong> Une chose-rat a 30 % de chances de conna&icirc;tre 1D3 sorts. Ceux qui avaient appris des sorts dans leur vie ant&eacute;rieure en conservent la connaissance. Une chose-rat, don d&rsquo;un Dieu Ext&eacute;rieur ou d&rsquo;une autre entit&eacute; de ce type, conna&icirc;t certainement de nombreux autres sorts.</p>\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p><strong>Attaques par round : </strong>1</p>\n<p><strong>Options de Combat rapproch&eacute; : </strong>Les choses-rats attaquent en grimpant sur les jambes ou les v&ecirc;tements de leurs adversaires humains, ou en se laissant tomber du plafond. Si elles parviennent &agrave; mordre, elles s&rsquo;accrochent &agrave; leur proie et continuent &agrave; lui infliger des dommages. Arracher une chose-rat fix&eacute;e &agrave; sa proie fait perdre &agrave; cette derni&egrave;re 1D3 points de vie.</p>\n<p><strong>Protection : </strong>Aucune, mais les attaques contre une chose-rat en pleine course subissent un d&eacute; malus.</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Rat-Thing.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Chose-rat","displayName":0,"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Mythos%20Monsters/Rat-Thing.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"oGUilfb1xc3NJzK3","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"kXvEkNlVrxoDCZDO","name":"Combat rapproché","type":"skill","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":"35","attributes":{},"properties":{"combat":true,"fighting":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":100000,"flags":{},"effects":[]},{"_id":"4Jol5eUFbUrHnPuq","name":"Morsure","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"Creature's natural attack","chat":"Creature's natural attack","special":""},"wpnType":"innate","skill":{"main":{"name":"Fighting","id":"kXvEkNlVrxoDCZDO"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""}},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"long":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"